Flask app

initial tutorial (part one): https://scotch.io/tutorials/build-a-crud-web-app-with-python-and-flask-part-one

Initialize variables at first
    export FLASK_CONFIG=development
    export FLASK_APP=run.py
    export FLASK_DEBUG=1

